# skill-doctor.tape — vhs script for the skill-doctor demo GIF.

Output "demos/skill-doctor.gif"

Set Theme "GitHub Dark"
Set FontFamily "JetBrains Mono"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1180
Set Height 780
Set Padding 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Framerate 24

Hide
Type "clear && bash demos/scenario-skill-doctor.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 16s
